Colloquially, we have some understanding of these.

36
00:02:03,131 --> 00:02:05,512
When we try to nail down very strict definitions,

37
00:02:05,572 --> 00:02:07,632
it can often turn out that they lead

38
00:02:07,652 --> 00:02:08,852
to counterintuitive results.

39
00:02:09,892 --> 00:02:11,213
And I think that's a problem.

40
00:02:12,808 --> 00:02:15,010
Exactly how to define it, we're not

41
00:02:15,050 --> 00:02:17,091
going to be too careful with.

42
