283
00:14:28,065 --> 00:14:31,507
Another way to say that your skills is harder to measure

284
00:14:31,847 --> 00:14:34,288
is that you get less payoff in terms of your victories

285
00:14:34,328 --> 00:14:35,288
for the same amount of skill.

286
00:14:40,508 --> 00:14:45,771
So when you add luck to a game and you make skill harder

287
00:14:45,811 --> 00:14:47,372
to measure, what's happened?

288
00:14:47,432 --> 00:14:48,013
Is that bad?

289
00:14:49,354 --> 00:14:53,476
It may very well be bad, because maybe your players

290
00:14:53,676 --> 00:14:56,678
expect a very high payoff for the amount of skill

291
00:14:56,698 --> 00:14:57,779
that they've acquired at the game.

292
00:14:57,819 --> 00:15:00,080
They have, after all, put a lot of effort into it.

293
00:15:01,481 --> 00:15:05,244
And key to understanding this is understanding

294
00:15:05,264 --> 00:15:08,326
what the value proposition of your game is for your players.

295
00:15:10,667 --> 00:15:14,174
For instance, if you're playing a competitive game

296
00:15:15,075 --> 00:15:17,019
and there's some payoff or skill.

297
00:15:18,517 --> 00:15:21,837
As those players continue to play that game or that genre

298
00:15:21,857 --> 00:15:25,658
of games over time, and they put more and more time and effort

299
00:15:25,718 --> 00:15:27,939
into mastering that game, they may very well

300
00:15:27,999 --> 00:15:30,659
expect a higher and higher payoff for their skill.

301
00:15:31,440 --> 00:15:35,220
And that's how you get things like fighting games becoming

302
00:15:35,280 --> 00:15:36,821
more and more skill testing over time.

303
00:15:37,201 --> 00:15:39,521
If you're a dedicated customer of these sorts of things,

304
00:15:39,881 --> 00:15:43,822
again, for a competitive game, where inherently in the setup

305
00:15:43,982 --> 00:15:46,943
it's you versus the other person on an emotional level

306
00:15:47,123 --> 00:15:47,603
as well as.

307
00:15:48,684 --> 00:15:49,744
sort of a rules level.

308
00:15:51,666 --> 00:15:55,109
It's not unlikely that you're going to be very upset

309
00:15:55,349 --> 00:15:57,690
when your payoff for skill gets lowered.

